    <h1>My Favorite Hobby: Photography</h1>
    <h2>Why I Love Photography</h2>
    <p>
        Photography lets me <strong>capture moments</strong> that would otherwise be lost. 
        It's amazing how a single photo can bring back <em>hundreds of memories</em>. 
        The best part is that <span class="highlight">anyone can start</span> with just a phone camera.
    </p>
    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <p>
        You don't need expensive gear to begin. Start by learning composition and lighting. 
        Practice daily and you'll see improvement fast. Photography has taught me patience 
        and how to see beauty in ordinary things.
    </p>
